{"nodes":[{"nodeID":"796","text":"Nuclear bombs should not be casually re-engineered for ordinary battlefield use.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:20:04"},{"nodeID":"2095","text":"If  the U.S. re-engeneer nuclear bombs it causes their threshold for nuclear weapons use to appear to lower","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:24:39"},{"nodeID":"2096","text":"It is plasuble that Pakistan and India lower their thresold as well","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:24:39"},{"nodeID":"2097","text":"If a state lowers the threshold of use the possibilities of the use increase","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:24:39"},{"nodeID":"2098","text":"a chief objective of American policy is to make sure these weapons are never used.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:24:39"},{"nodeID":"2099","text":"The lowering of the nuclear weapons threshold causes other states to lower it as well","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:24:39"},{"nodeID":"2100","text":"countries like Pakistan India and probably North Korea have added nuclear weapons to their arsenals","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:24:39"},{"nodeID":"2101","text":"Washington must be wary of appearing to lower the psychological threshold for nuclear weapons use","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:24:39"},{"nodeID":"2102","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:24:40","scheme":"CauseToEffect","schemeID":"4"},{"nodeID":"2103","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:24:40","scheme":"PracticalReasoning","schemeID":"28"},{"nodeID":"2104","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:24:40","scheme":"CauseToEffect","schemeID":"4"}],"edges":[{"edgeID":"2025","fromID":"2095","toID":"2102","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2026","fromID":"2102","toID":"2101","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2027","fromID":"2096","toID":"2103","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2028","fromID":"2097","toID":"2103","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2029","fromID":"2098","toID":"2103","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2030","fromID":"2103","toID":"796","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2031","fromID":"2099","toID":"2104","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2032","fromID":"2100","toID":"2104","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2033","fromID":"2101","toID":"2104","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2034","fromID":"2104","toID":"2096","formEdgeID":null}],"locutions":[{"nodeID":"796","personID":"1238","timestamp":"2015-10-14 15:21:10","start":null,"end":null,"source":null}]}